name: CalorieQuick
0:
”Alexa, open calorie quick”
”Alexa, ask calorie quick how many calories do broccoli have”
”Alexa, ask calorie quick calories in hamburger”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: calorie quick
des:
This skill is made to quickly give you a sense of how many calories various foods have. There are no special account or hardware requirements that you need to use the skill, so please go ahead and try it out!
This skill will recognize fruits, vegetables, most popular american dishes, and many branded, processed foods.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
